@startuml
title Lab 6 Part 2 - Reporting Data Flow
left to right direction

rectangle "NtcSensor" as NTC
rectangle "DhtSensor" as DHT
rectangle "AnalogConditioner\nfor each channel" as COND
rectangle "MonitorApp" as APP
rectangle "LcdDisplay" as LCD
rectangle "printf /\nStdioBridge" as STDIO

NTC --> COND
DHT --> COND
COND --> APP : raw / sat / med / avg
APP --> LCD : filtered values
APP --> STDIO : diagnostics

note bottom of APP
Updates threshold from potentiometer
and may drive alert outputs
end note

@enduml
